ed;\">並不容許私家車登島</span>，於2014年放寬的士可全日於馬灣上行駛，貨車則可在每日10時至4時行駛。"},{"pid":"2e0ac7703bfc4aa471c9e5ed35a9a659a00b2501","tid":713592,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:38:41.000Z","msg":"馬灣一係巴士，一係call 的士，一係船，巴士唔計通宵最遠去到荃灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c89cfc795a59db0d6e078fb34a1fd79a9d9b44f","tid":713592,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"咁有米揸tesla咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad6458139bf5016569fb2abe2c39f24302acc23","tid":713592,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c89cfc795a59db0d6e078fb34a1fd79a9d9b44f","tid":713592,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"咁有米揸tesla咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:47:18.000Z","msg":"你又真心定假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n馬灣唔入得私家車"},{"pid":"159b8060447154ef3c1242ec59568ba7837e9177","tid":713592,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ad6458139bf5016569fb2abe2c39f24302acc23","tid":713592,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c89cfc795a59db0d6e078fb34a1fd79a9d9b44f","tid":713592,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"咁有米揸tesla咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:47:18.000Z","msg":"你又真心定假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n馬灣唔入得私家車"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:48:48.000Z","msg":"的士都入得&hellip;私人屋苑自己傾掂佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaee15ee7c073dec0b903dfd862bc7941406c7e7","tid":713592,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"159b8060447154ef3c1242ec59